    "body": "It sounds like you have something very unusual going on with your OSX installation.  Have you installed any special GPU drivers or other OS modifications?\n\nThe \"Fullscreen\" mode uses the old-school modal fullscreen behaviour, which will override and disable mission control / spaces / returning to desktop.\n\nThe \"Pseudo-fullscreen\" mode integrates with OSX's native fullscreening behaviour, so integrates properly with mission control and spaces.\n"
  },
